description:
New to chromakey? Start creating amazing photos or videos today with help from TubeTape.com's Chromakey Tips and Tricks tutorial. This video will show you step by step how to create professional chromakey composites. Learn quickly as we walk you through the fundamentals of lighting your set, setting up your chromakey screen, basic camera functions, and the tools necessary to get the polished look you want from your projects. We will also mention the challenges you may face when shooting or editing chromakey &amp; how to avoid them. Popular chromakey software for photo and video is also featured in this video to give you an idea of which software may be right for you.


